有事物的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/903Jctw6yyiIOehetQPjyonNndkwBPH3gnNpF38fhdqmPY8Ion7KG4pjweDMpnuI_hxfxL4cniU4XWpbh19NzjbUpEVeoWWCZWB4F4fFvvI1WoZyPiOR9aThpjMSHHjzj4mhR8EjOgCtwxTEeL3eVJ5fS7An0rtZjO7z8CLSelkmrvj_Ky0rTMpQDShlutur2_jg7_i-gxXLymxFJlfRciCIBT-Ffs_oZHezaKyH0D8u_wkzNVtEnXCwnCuA02IFsazi4Lwdn99tBUr4jVrPm4HmkKrG6t9EeX6o7eARMnzrZzGp11JaoB_xoxxB0DqZpHSlJBm_PyMRdll_5o39BI1r77EFdG8m4dGDD-2l4XCUoZb13nOAdA4L_w/HSMD6i8tfvsFqkjsn0Dk91w5pZCyjGak/7" title="美国的主要供应商"&gt;主要供应商&lt;/a&gt;，越南官员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/NAQVaxiA79HpFBhJFJbdTd1ePUOXHns7neIdOSGlqwC4IxCUkaGjydyy-b934YrjHBoa6RKev21dVv3dQKF5_S2fYChc05XkLY8AHfbom3u71l_87h3NBk5z0PGrK4pl6jcrkvvaMB0xVrd4wi7c0PMmHVkDDX8SKlLsnvdRDpzLe8IF5EyDyyj8N4N0xZ-BiMAfoTW80MIstwplLQQFCgIRyEF4_S06g-Rw58FDursGmGUOQDv_FysVM33TktA41etSkjTrk1cxIVY6HlHXY1P6YZ-nj1MDMxVxQf0CVW6xdksBgq02PLLZU6hZqbkJhnYStLvNipDYVELnfdIy3jZ3j4hXXGz4HAGeepgkBDJ6I60uP8PMnrUA3A/e4481oHWBa9z5nx9wxvYwMOYpg0JNS8c/7" title="不懈地工作"&gt;不懈地工作了&lt;/a&gt;几个月，以避免我们的关税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ey4weF7dkBirAaGSOlKAIEWsHBdRXFv0HcvlMsGrfSfNDFYZEIn9p8viHzNlmRd_pELU24nv1bMDZcaiQcFF7fBuZoE_GpN8O1kZhDWdxvzMZkWqYBr1rfw5aVZpSxA7N9oLEgb_xwH45xkjMuQDtzZf9w-fVLUIB3aZvp9dOrz7hcEwFN0wtG8QNoVtOxgif_axUfcyDq6RD7PGl2M2lviQddGYC0YKLnNMa94vxEo6ifPYULK60DAm864nKcGBzjygLC9sQ5e__vHLwWtKYdx2VhpMQ-7-SYzLBIiTSPUIoum-9sjOwpEkrvcMBJJzeBT7-QLKTA3OQVvSBU80uJK7FcA6CDVIEKeYFGVJ1Tu0kZ6gfblfq2IrAQ/x86Y2w73P7fyf7oiKSUKWA9X47978Ohy/7" title="被46％的征税击中"&gt;无论如何，他们都受到46％的税率&lt;/a&gt;，在大约60个国家 /地区与其他东南亚国家的最高税率中，他们首当其冲的唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7ZKeVV2UknXZREmXVK6wg9EYlnNtseDqFySMP46R6xNXD8jg_WszyBsJBfWY04zzerbtgPCovjN12ZI7RoJYzdkAIA0MZS1R1ERR1CoTRKlPTAyQAi0phtcDVMNSiyxlgV423AeCP-aTCLeLnpl84jAW0-5OEOGbKMU_BP3rlY8AcImUTXIBCPqUXSbfn5j7PPoPLKCURjktcm9AdCpEVCrAubqxxLHjmlWXGrg9RMju9lxncfGG3sJZpCXRjcrYJrNDacJFfaWsIGZIO1DoY_h5ZupZYP8vlun3U23e95Bgk5RjPXyUjK4_Kuup0iX8w0hbRroA2MyU13j9DPyZdfc9GE_AA4tdBwfGY_x5nbzUm611svhR90SbkQ/cjbsq86b30FKgFEb5kI2PNBBVW3iEIl5/7" title="互惠关税"&gt;互惠关税&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWCOM4scd8F4/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWCOM4scd8F4/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;特朗普在周三在白宫玫瑰园的关税中宣布。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：肯特·尼西村（Kent Nishimura）/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;越南与美国，仅次于中国和墨西哥的美国经营第三高的贸易盈余。官员们承诺通过消除贸易壁垒和进口美国能源来纠正差距。总理菲姆·明·奇恩（PhạmMinhChính）表示，国家航空公司正在考虑花费数十亿美元的波音喷气机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;最后，这还不够，强调了该地区&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OFq7qSw-f6M6gg2r7_h--Xu5TYEKcxpSXqe2pVF6B3bMC5Aa7z8OoFGr38vaPPRx-mFKNWxl0tfqollD-XARRFsHjWLW4hFK31lNylq3FmIW5QHuiePNs7ga9r4HkorqTJWL95KgHMeisH9peWUcINkOo7EVGJAYMzJjDFB8t0oMBsNzWoAHqV3w7aU7cPDeq_h7JDWjOIiuFUe0Z3KRAB5ilrN0VZ5BEY_7T_CWn6subHupCRZg_Jym3kNq9ts0_7JtG1gNx6c3j8JDXhXJOZ1NkC8cJIvhJ_K1tvkLKSgP-oAEbHNbGOLdrPb33imIcHXqh_etecDWbOZRz_ku98BL-9sISeyiUamTeusodtCkai2Y0MfC2i_zMVY/ZIEGyk25PCaUfrO-aXPKRep_xWtAyLX4/7" title="试图安抚特朗普"&gt;试图安抚特朗普&lt;/a&gt;的障碍。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;柬埔寨面临任何亚洲经济中最高的个人关税，占49％，承诺将某些美国商品的利率从35％降低至5％。印度尼西亚征收32％的印度尼西亚，承诺放松贸易规则，并将代表团派往华盛顿。马来西亚作为东南亚国家协会现任主席，将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/chBOWYVLZAojsq4U_JhzwwRVN0TavnW_dWQEOeukJWswL6hmkc2JgQ5HaVW2SKExztKQUQ5_9n9dKAj5SvtuMKs15Nl1RVeIkdZ3VlWXImbATZrAXt5OvMxsB-FKydshdoOEU150ccdhTz2kDPKC_