;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUGs9FoGvRNk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUGs9FoGvRNk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;“加沙的和平前景看起来越来越黯淡……&lt;/strong&gt; [内塔尼亚胡]坚决他不会停下来直到哈马斯放下武器和加沙的塞德斯力量。很有可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0VDbpOrqqGxsz5UlAsTou_wVlBMwfmW4QG7L7Un5Pq_UeWYEEz9pItDNtfs-Ua7kNnNcsZYKkSSX647rJjxMr3coOfpVUvBjunYILKfqkPzEAz7bjmJchKG0rqfd490DNU8J5ex1vic_cUYY2eFx3I8wEi0VfulI9XxZ4myS0UMgbGM6-HPLUgdeg24oPGvzGLpt0QU_bUlqXVTw4dpsTgGvJnvKn1xJ4Dq3vlMvVl3pM1EYqPAGAJ2FJ6O3-CYJNjt8QfnYpu7zPFb2scDAB-k8A-5mRCS_nzIQnH5UrUriUYvaMeffshx3SGX-NLAMhtHnm50X2uXyOjbxeMK-EyQ_LsZ3iSrA83om4oicdsM-aYPNo5HYwRUbAw0/YiXvTe6psnFafYD__Z8tVatzxesKMX8c/7" title="随着内塔尼亚胡（Netanyahu）的按下"&gt;很快就会发生&lt;/a&gt;。” &lt;em&gt;- 票价Alghoul， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GYDnl9XC0MCstAfGBDbIuw6NLCIWwMlkb19g6BdWhJ3EK5zIOBID16CtCkbds4I1-OHnLWnIxlPfLHt5i3dOpJ0qMW4hHn-5V8KGCAVrIOfBVfhWxB3D4lzlSOWSKySD1ofusknbFtfPIh4_Bgz6h4edskMo-_DeSKBYwO6ea2Kfx9FD2rLWq7l4CZgW1dCOH5UVi3NH_vRjVYulE8In7mGbQpLVN_yhV-smQ_ViGS6ovo8OBV2tjYXyXPKVn4qrl9Fpirq54FHY18KRSQJDiDPT1kRX-E9JbDDuAnKp3tf_cccD8ljGJdHnNTO5QAfWFpY4jK0yMbb4DqfZDr6k6-6xxc3jElS__1YAnY_f5ZS6bsmhePcltWgM_d0/lwOdvd0mBJkp8R7W05g3dnkEXStIbNfj/7" title="力量平衡"&gt;电力通讯的平衡&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;借助&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iaNbtBks_IwzfSVaZmhnqWiedKkl98o126fLbCpwTLyIoBEgC