上鹰，但中国似乎取得了无懈可击的领先优势。电动汽车巨头比安特（Byd）最近宣布了一个电池，可以在短短5分钟内收取400公里的费用，中国汽车制造商越来越多地进入新兴市场。一直以来，全球贸易和关税的重新排列正在通过全球行业发动冲击波。本周，彭博社的全球汽车编辑克雷格·特鲁德尔（Craig Trudell）在《零》上揭开了电动汽车革命的最新曲折。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xDMU4VnJcBljQgcNWOHzWhupVZBZ1m4jylvUBaGvFvD0CQilLXqE9ezMkQKzNl4n66TN2dPTr6zV4dvRxKVpEWmdmI8ApiXdvxv0A0UtrtO-ACe43rJTw3lFJATSFTsVMIJaMW81t0HCVfuVv0jelIc76CT40OqT8PCUlAtU2f4Ydm8f9l9ZDPmSdXmDdrRWY1PKEBjhKYEAifCVi-phaqtX0pRqyK1V9XAzpU2qKkBsQv1ROZ48SCbZisk9HJN3mZqrkQFpS17D5Sl7R1XUuowazx0qxpB-mC8HFhc-ihIM0wNvsp0ncS7DKHp14_FTOsnP_Qq74119N4R88r4jkGZhIDdIsg8Cu4gb_3WarGE7Sps4_tU2cWZM7ws/UQZj4ixJ0Yonpau0ban5of938D2wNF71/7" target="_blank"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，然后在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XS614--67gn5mDC_KFU5yYtxUIARAzlJNPyUZaKMW-W9gOdPBbL6fqsxozTFWeJMisgyadkfcmPH4q5nV92sxmNyGFJ0mJm3IDVeXg8PdmDtaLmKtCwC-ksyFtkrIxL06DsRJ-iSSaNjmGQSgSNuwbIERpRAKgVZrIt1NvqgMbMo_gmiKmOtgm3JOSZUW4VbHPyZquh-TnROnYPvAqe4KdR2YCY2UZuNGTQSWNAplI9wpDliFQs7XzgbYptv2m97YjgRgik6FR5RdAIVdRiELo5C9hwneu0xJzYPgUvJOALGE5N6blRxoKMMsUcL9n1RSqFPBVYCjpJhe5e8FwAUY_mHezm7UWUB9H-8HXa5Yi1XnIDO1RC4DZVf4IVJGYxV3nYBfCowyDL0H3HFQXimshONR2bAsBdBTX6wz880aARQWPrLQwLdyEa_KSgg-kWnxl_s0IhDyddpHc-yUq8/oEH1Bpn6F7PZvYVkWsmGMF-mujhdPouo/7"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; ， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5-dqFg1qfN7SOVPr5Ra3_zvad36OOoq8Spf1X51Q0FL_zbaH8pKAm5tZfceZDt2OMLX5NIg3C2LYi6jA-P4I45k6W84tmoMzzZaLnuzIxtrabOMlLG38ER6eNV9JZhX3TyQa8cgPjNFBy1nwX9OAyEkPbrRZJ8VPfYyATCLBnR7JBTUPPfpwGkNU7wvR5DnhH_83sSSu5h-FOXZ9pIBatCday0DTK6yUpm1s4ds1quFjRwNDflxijxdlDYNxYI0z0KD39OyfyQAzlbLGFs4ik1irk5uLUYxRg-DkoYTMsMO4Q-hzNUjxPGoHML0SE6bYXV3Rh8XzepvmX8BApA7dQEuYJqiwBzGE3Sky_v04WX-91buNi6LfIMTDvrOX9Q-pXdGvncUg94-9_Catt6ijkm1aFwYxwN6uIIJBZq5DFsNSIX5vreCYJVa7V2GjwExKZw4EDfxv5urpg57gi0T8e0ysSg6jTa69sOEQy59ghoY2EUSTgmr9YLVCYWp4fqm5/CL3sLIriGzhUxVAHSWN55gKgO5etBWC3/7"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/